snippet.title: Teen Sentenced To Four Months In Prison For Breaking Quarantine
snippet.description:
Teen Sentenced To Four Months In Prison For Breaking Quarantine
Subscribe Here ☛ http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/3qF38D7

There have been lockdowns and restrictions put into place all over the world, and though a lot of us are tired of it, its still important to follow the rules to keep yourself and your loved ones as safe as possible. So when you're travelling, its still important to self isolate and to monitor your symptoms and interactions with others, and above all, do not do what this girl did. Skylar Mack, a teenager from Georgia decided to travel to the Cayman Islands to visit her boyfriend and watch him compete in a Jet Ski competition.
